Events - Sundays in the Summer: Roller Skating
image:image.image:caption: Our Second Sundays in the Summer event will be held at Three Fountains Skating Rink on June 12 at 3:00 pm. Skating will be a fun activity for all ages where anyone and everyone is welcome. Cost of admission and food will not be provided.

image:image.image:title: Events - Sundays in the Summer: Fireflies Game
image:image.image:caption: Our third Sundays in the Summer event will be held at a Fireflies game on June 26th at 5:05 pm. We will al be sitting on the Berm supporting our Fireflies, anyone and everyone is welcome! Cost of admission and food will not be provided.

image:image.image:title: Events - Sundays in the Summer: Pool Party
image:image.image:caption: Our Fourth Sunday in the Summer event will be held at the Kingston Harbor pool and Clubhouse at 3:00 pm. We will be having a potluck style meal so please bring your best dish so that we can eat, splash and be family!

image:image.image:title: Events - Sundays in the Summer: Bowling
image:image.image:caption: Our fifth Sundays in the Summer event will be held at JC's Lexington Bowling Alley on July 24th at 3:00 pm. Our Bowling day will be a fun activity for the whole family, anyone and everyone is welcome ! Admission will not be provided.

image:image.image:title: Events - Sundays in the Summer: Picnic
image:image.image:caption: Our final Sundays in the Summer event will be held at Virginia Hylton park at 5:00 pm. We will be having a picnic as a church family, anyone and everyone is welcome! Come help us say goodbye to a great summer! This picnic is BYOF - Bring Your Own Food.
